{"tid":2411742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求求你地唔好妥協，要抵制安心出行","createTime":"2021-02-17T14:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T14:54:00.000Z","uid":35266,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eda13ca74ac7759daf9cabaa1a45c28b33765aad","tid":2411742,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:20:02.000Z","msg":"係講緊扮嘟左都唔應該<br />\n一年前大家仲講緊不合作運動<br />\n講緊要增加政權管治成本<br />\n但點解一年之後，連抵制安心出行呢樣咁無成本既事都唔肯做？<br />\n唔用好困難咩？無堂食、無戲院、無gym room已經講緊幾個月既事，香港人咪一樣咁過<br />\n點解宜家就唔可以忍多陣，等班商家佬仆街番一頭半個月，由商家佬迫政府收番條例？<br />\n<br />\n搞黨鐵可能話驚俾人拉<br />\n罷工又話驚俾人秋後算帳<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">請問唔用安心出行會有咩後果？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可能好多人以為運動冷卻左，可以回歸港豬mode, 唔再需要做任何野<br />\n但革命從來都唔係一朝一夕既事，大家再抱住功利主義，覺得有用先去做，又唔肯長期付出，最後只會攬住一齊死。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我求求大家，<span class=\"red\">唔可以扮嘟，寫名都唔好寫</span>，要班參加安心出行既舖頭陷家產<br />\n幫幫手參與下呢個難得可以做到既不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4950030d5c2165015f5ca93cb3179fa2058b5f","tid":2411742,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decbe750881ec754b6f08ff2c555816039f84894","tid":2411742,"uid":54291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:24:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a1101662a6965da126611c1c1061776c3c78d008","tid":2411742,"uid":35266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"抗爭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dff16793435fd6e031af88f2516544cee59741","tid":2411742,"uid":239539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:32:34.000Z","msg":"寫名都唔好寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪諗住走精面"},{"pid":"911809cf4212ef180c8f4771b3ba1a16b515a6c5","tid":2411742,"uid":35266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6dff16793435fd6e031af88f2516544cee59741","tid":2411742,"uid":239539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:32:34.000Z","msg":"寫名都唔好寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪諗住走精面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:35:08.000Z","msg":"走精面只會好似支那咁<br />\n俾人慢慢逐樣ban, ban到無哂自由為止"},{"pid":"b25003df76814881751f2f6e3d614f3123ec509f","tid":2411742,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"咪撚裝呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c3caf7c04d1c59c7af98d38053fb1c47f3af9c","tid":2411742,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:48:22.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚贏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />維穩成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9593642d0e2a2201c78d4dfb18f56a81f1f84db1","tid":2411742,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6c3caf7c04d1c59c7af98d38053fb1c47f3af9c","tid":2411742,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:48:22.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚贏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />維穩成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"唔關恐懼撚事<br />\n係因為大家都覺得抵制無用，隔離果個唔會做<br />\n所以就一齊接受，一齊食屎"}]}